    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1903-11-05T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1903-11-05T00:00:00-05:00" n="234"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d234">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Ehrman</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Panama</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1903-11-05">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 5, 1903</hi>.</date>
                        <lb/>(Received 12.50 p.m.)</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Received an official circular letter from the committee of the provisional
                    government saying that on 4th political move occurred, and the Department of
                    Panama withdraws from the Republic of the United States of Colombia and formed
                    the Republic of Panama.</p>
                <p>Requested to acknowledge the receipt of circular letter.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Ehrman.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
